(185, NULL, 'oryx', NULL, '-', 28, 216, 'info@oryxenergies.com', 225514000, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Tan House, Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.oryxenergies.com', '-', '20240806132908.jpg', 'The Oryx brand is well-known in Tanzania, where it is a market leader in fuels, LPG and lubricants distribution.\r\n\r\nOryx Energies offers an integrated supply, storage and distribution model, providing a full range of products and services to domestic and industrial customers. These include fuels sourcing, strategic storage facilities, wholesale distribution, retail service stations, LPG storage, filling and distribution, high quality lubricants from our own blending plant, and a full range of products and services for commercial and industrial clients (including on-site management and logistics).\r\n\r\nWe have been present in the country since 1999, when Oryx acquired Agip’s assets in the country. The size of the country and its strategic port in the capital, Dar es Salaam, make Tanzania an important market and point of access to East Africa, including the landlocked Great Lakes countries. Over the years, we have continued to invest and expand in the country and in East Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-06 18:29:08', '2024-08-06 18:29:08'),
(186, NULL, 'River oil petroleum hq', NULL, '-', 28, 216, 'dg@pura.go.tz', 754277716, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Kenyatta Rd, Mwanza', 'https://www.pura.go.tz', '-', '', 'The Petroleum Upstream Regulatory Authority (PURA), is the regulatory authority established under Section 11 of the Petroleum Act, 2015 (Act No. 21 of 2015) with the mandate to regulate and monitor petroleum upstream operations and LNG activities in the Mainland Tanzania and providing advisory services to the Government and the Minister responsible for petroleum affairs.\r\n\r\nThe mandate is underpinned in several Policy and legal instruments including: the National Energy Policy, 2015; the Petroleum Act, 2015; the Oil and Gas Revenue Management Act, 2015 and the Tanzania Extractive Industries (Transparency and Accountability) Act, 2015. The Oil and Gas Revenue Management Act of 2015 requires PURA to carry out or cause to be carried out costs and revenues audit of the petroleum operations. The Extractive Industry (Transparence and Accountability) Act, 2015 also requires PURA to observe transparency and accountability in its undertakings. PURA mandates is further derived from the National Energy Policy, 2015 which gives guidance on establishment of upstream regulator to effectively and efficiently manage petroleum upstream operations.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-06 18:47:45', '2024-08-06 18:47:45'),
(187, NULL, 'Dawasco house', NULL, '-', 28, 216, 'info@dawasa.go.tz', 222760006, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Dar es Salaam Water Supply And Sanitation Authority (DAWASA)  Jamhuri ya Muungano wa Tanzania  DAWASA YETU BUILDING, P.O Box 1573, DSM', 'https://www.dawasa.go.tz', '-', '20240806142119.png', 'In 1981, the government established the National Urban Water Authority (NUWA) and charged it with the responsibility to develop and manage urban water supply on Tanzania Mainland. NUWA, which became operational in 1984, set a target to take over and reform water supply services in all urban areas in Dar es Salaam. The government re-organized NUWA in 1997 to form the Dar es Salaam Water and Sewerage Authority by merging the functions of NUWA and the sewerage functions of the Sewerage and Sanitation Department of the City Commission. Under the DAWASA Act, DAWASA was made responsible for operating and maintaining all water supply and sewerage services in Dar es Salaam and its satellite towns of Bagamoyo and Kibaha.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-06 19:21:19', '2024-08-06 19:21:19'),
(188, NULL, 'Ewura head office', NULL, '-', 28, 216, 'info@ewura.go.tz', 262329003, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'EWURA CENTRAL ZONE · First Floor, · 3 EWURA Street, · 41104 Tambukareli, · P.O Box 2857, · Dodoma, Tanzania', 'www.ewura.go.tz', NULL, '20240806143152.gif', 'The Energy and Water Utilities Regulatory Authority (EWURA) is an autonomous multi-sectoral regulatory authority established by the EWURA Act Cap 414 of the laws of Tanzania. It is responsible for technical and economic regulation of the electricity, petroleum, natural gas and water sectors in Tanzania pursuant to Cap 414 and sector legislation.\r\nThe Energy and Water Utilities Regulatory Authority (EWURA) is an autonomous multi-sectoral regulatory authority established by the EWURA Act Cap 414 of the laws of Tanzania. It is responsible for technical and economic regulation of the electricity, petroleum, natural gas and water sectors in Tanzania pursuant to Cap 414 and sector legislation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-06 19:31:52', '2024-08-06 19:31:52'),
(189, NULL, 'CENTRAL MARKET ARUSHA', NULL, '-', 29, 216, 'singida@psssf.go.tz', 679514293, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Quartier Sokoine, Entre Somali Rd., Bondeni st. et Azimio St., Arusha, Tanzania', 'https://tz.geoview.info › soko_kuu', '-', '', 'The large covered market in Arusha is 1km west of the Clock Tower and 300m south of the National Bus Station. There is a paid car park on the Somali Road side, not far away. And of course a maze of stalls that obey a precise geographical distribution between fruit and vegetables, meat, fish, clothes, fabrics or even sandals made of truck tires, 100% Masaai. Beware of the inevitable pickpockets.\r\nThe traditional market square is a city square where traders set up stalls and buyers browse the merchandise. This kind of market is very old, and countless such markets are still in operation around the whole world. In some places markets are held in buildings called market halls', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-06 20:08:26', '2024-08-06 20:08:26'),
(190, NULL, 'Awure boutique resort,Dar es Salaam', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'support@scantrip.com', 753555551, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Mbezi Beach, Africana Road 111, Dar es salaam, Dar es Salaam Region, Tanzania', 'https://planetofhotels.com › tanzania', '-', '20240808081910.jpg', 'Property Location When you stay at Azure Boutique Resort in Dar es Salaam, you\'ll be close to Bongoyo Island. \r\nThis 4-star resort is within the vicinity of Lugalo Golf Course and Mwenge Carvers Market. \r\nRooms Make yourself at home in one of the 37 individually decorated guestrooms, featuring microwaves and flat-screen televisions. \r\nComplimentary wireless Internet access keeps you connected, and satellite programming is available for your entertainment. \r\nBathrooms have showers and complimentary toiletries. Conveniences include safes and desks, and housekeeping is provided daily. \r\nAmenities Be sure to enjoy recreational amenities including an outdoor pool and a 24-hour fitness center. Additional features at this resort include complimentary wireless Internet access, wedding services, and a television in a common area. \r\nDining Enjoy a meal at the restaurant or snacks in the coffee shop/café. The resort also offers room service (during limited hours). Relax with a refreshing drink at one of the 3 bars/lounges. \r\nA complimentary cooked-to-order breakfast is served daily from 7:00 AM to 11:00 AM. Business, Other Amenities Featured amenities include a business center, dry cleaning/laundry services, and a 24-hour front desk. Planning an event in Dar es Salaam? This resort has facilities measuring 3016 square feet (280 square meters), including a conference center. \r\nA roundtrip airport shuttle is provided for a surcharge (available 24 hours), and free self parking is available onsite.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 13:19:10', '2024-08-08 13:19:10'),
(191, NULL, 'Ramada resort', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@ramadaresortdar.com', 222162333, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '170 - 171 Africana Road Jangwani Beach Dar es Salaam TZ, Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.ramadaresortdar.com', '-', '20240808082543.jpg', 'Welcome to Ramada Resort by Wyndham Dar Es Salaam, your premier oceanfront retreat on Jangwani Beach. Indulge in a luxurious escape with our world-class amenities and services designed for both leisure and business travelers. Explore the unparalleled beauty of the Indian Ocean with these exceptional features.\r\nExplore diverse flavors at our restaurants and bars. From fine dining to a cozy coffee spot or a trendy bar, enjoy tasty African and international dishes. Treat yourself to signature cocktails and premium wines for a complete culinary experience.\r\nRelax and unwind by our dazzling outdoor pool — a serene oasis with stunning ocean views. Enjoy the perfect poolside retreat, complete with comfy sun loungers and gently swaying palm trees.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 13:25:43', '2024-08-08 13:25:43'),
(192, NULL, 'Jangwani sea breez', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'gm@jangwaniseabreezeresort.co.tz', 786800870, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'White Sands Road, Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.jangwaniseabreezeresort.co.tz', '-', '20240808083855.jpg', 'A LITTLE ABOUT US.\r\n Jangwani Sea Breeze Beach Resort is situated on the mainland of Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, along Mbezi Beach on beautiful crystal white sand; a 25 minutes drive away from the city center, the Resort is situated on either side of Africana road. The hotel is divided into two parts, exclusive residence courtyard with its own private pool and bar for the in house guest only. All rooms are ensuite with LCD TV, Split AC, Electronic safe & walk in showers. Full English breakfast is served from 6am to 11am in courtyard. Tea/coffee facilities are available in each room together with free beach slippers. Complimentary 2 bottles of water are supplied daily per room and with free room service from our beach restaurant. Courtyard bar is open 24 hours for our in house guest and snacks round the clock. The hotel on the other side has public area with entertainment facilities. We have children’s pool, adult’s pool, toddler’s pool with GYM and SPA. The beach has sports facilities including beach volley ball, beach football, children’s swings, slides & much more. Beach beds are complimentary on sand and on terrazzo. There is a beach shop & arcade game room offering all types of goodies, play stations, pool table, table tennis, & various card games are also available at zero charge. There are 2 restaurants & bars serving exotic drinks, international cocktails, shooters, local/ imported beers with many varieties of mouth watering food. And on weekends Special Buffet and Live Barbeque. There is a light music played from Monday to Friday together with rain dance and DJ spinning live every Saturday and Sunday from 5pm to 11pm. 3 star price for 5 star values.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 13:38:55', '2024-08-08 13:38:55'),
(193, NULL, 'Hotel slipway', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'reception@hotelslipway.com', 222600893, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Yacht Club Rd,Masaki, Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.hotelslipway.com', '-', '20240808085252.png', 'Slipway Road, Msasani Peninsula, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania, Masaki, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania. Facing the beachfront, Hotel Slipway offers 4-star accommodation in Dar es Salaam and has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness centre and terrace. The property features a bar, as well as a restaurant serving Mediterranean cuisine. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.\r\nThe hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, a kettle, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a shared bathroom with a shower. Some rooms have a kitchenette with a microwave. At Hotel Slipway rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels.\r\nGuests at the accommodation can enjoy a buffet or a continental breakfast.\r\nHotel Slipway offers a children\'s playground. The area is popular for hiking and cycling, and car hire is available at the hotel.\r\nPopular points of interest near Hotel Slipway include Msasani Beach, Yacht Club Beach and Coco Beach. The nearest airport is Julius Nyerere International Airport, 17 km from the accommodation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 13:52:52', '2024-08-08 13:52:52'),
(194, NULL, 'White sands hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@hotelwhitesands.com', 758818697, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Africana Road Dar es Salaam TZ, 3030', 'https://hotelwhitesands.com', '-', '20240808085806.png', 'The White Sands Resort and Conference Centre is situated on an idyllic private beach, just 25km north of Dar es Salaam and Julius Nyerere International Airport. Dar es Salaam means ‘abode of peace’ and it is no surprise that guests start to relax and feel at peace as soon as they enter the reception of the White Sands Resort and Conference Centre. The resort is on Mbezi Beach, one of the long white sandy beaches that makes Tanzania a haven for beach lovers. The decor contributes to the feeling of being in paradise.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 13:58:06', '2024-08-08 13:58:06'),
(195, NULL, 'Sunrise beach resort', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@sunrisebeachresort.co.tz', 755400900, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Mjimwema, Dar es Salaam, Tanzania', 'https://sunrisebeachresort.com', '-', '', 'Situated along a sandy beach on the Indian Ocean coastline, Sunrise Beach Resort offers a variety of water sports, a spa, and a restaurant and bar. The thatched-roof buildings are set in a garden with palm trees.\r\nEach room includes a private bathroom with free toiletries. Most rooms also come with a balcony, satellite TV, minibar and tea-and-coffee making facilities.\r\nGuests can relax by the beach or at the spa. They can also enjoy water sports, such as scuba diving, wind surfing and water skiing. Trips to nearby islands can also be arranged. Featuring panoramic sea views, the open-air restaurant offers both a la carte and buffet dishes.\r\nSunrise Beach Resort is located 6 km from Mjimwema and 35 km from the Dar Es Salaam city centre. Julius Nyerere International Airport can be reached within a 50-minute drive.\r\nDistance in property description is calculated using © OpenStreetMap', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 14:09:39', '2024-08-08 14:09:39'),
(196, NULL, 'South beach resort', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@southbeachresort-tz.com', 684111852, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Kigamboni Bridge, Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.instagram.com › southbeachresort_tz', '-', '', 'Located in the Kigamboni area or better known as South Beach, features an exclusive location on the Indian Ocean front. It is located comfortably away from the hustle and bustle of the city, 8 kms from the Kigamboni ferry.Thirty-six (36) well furnished, air conditioned rooms with one double bed and one single bed in each room. Every room also offers a private balcony overlooking the Indian Ocean.South Beach Resort is the perfect location and environment to cater to all your functions from Birthday Parties, corporate day-out parties, corporate team building events and entire company family day out events up to 4000 people! Our premises facilitates and supports the company\'s goals, whether it is to bring departments closer together, or to provide excellent entertainment and catering to the entire staff and their loved ones. our state of the art conference centre equipped with all the essential technology, stationary and comfort is the best in South Beach which can accommodate up to four (4) different conferences at once or open up into one large hall for up to 400 people. The conference hall can also be converted and decorated to host amazing, memorable wedding parties!', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 14:17:47', '2024-08-08 14:17:47'),
(197, NULL, 'New Hotel Dodoma', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@newdodomahotel.com', 262321641, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, '239 Oposite dodoma railway station TZ, Dodoma 41110', 'https://newdodomahotel.com-tanzania.com › ...', '-', '', 'The News Dodoma Hotel is situated opposite the train station in central Dodoma. It offers an outdoor pool, a lush garden, free Wi-Fi and private parking.\r\nThe rooms are fitted with a satellite TV and en suite bathrooms. Most of the rooms have air conditioning. The Executive rooms and the Suites also have a seating area.\r\nThe hotel has a sports bar and 3 restaurants, serving local and International cuisine.\r\nOther facilities and services at New Dodoma Hotel include a massage and fitness centre, conference facilities and concierge services.\r\nThe hotel is a 6-minute drive from the Parliament Buildings and a 10-minute drive from Dodoma Airport. Transfer services can be arranged for a fee.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 14:24:28', '2024-08-08 14:24:28'),
(198, NULL, 'Royal village hotel Dodoma', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'royalvillage@hotmail.com', 768224142, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Area D, Dodoma-Tanzania.', 'www.royalvillage.co.tz', '-', '', 'Royal Village Hotel Dodoma offers 55 rooms about 10 minutes\' stroll of Nyerere Square. There is an airport shuttle bus service, 24-hour front desk assistance and a laundry room available at this Dodoma hotel.\r\nLocated a short walk to Bunge Tanzania Parliament Buildings, the business property is set near University of Dodoma. The low-budget hotel can be reached within 25 minutes\' walk from Mirembe Mental Hospital.\r\nResidents can have breakfast in the restaurant. Pestana Pub serves a good range of African food and lies nearly 5 minutes\' walk away. The nearest bus stop is Hice za Mipango, 10 minutes\' walk away. Guests will appreciate live performances and karaoke organized at Royal Village Hotel.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 14:38:22', '2024-08-08 14:38:22'),
(199, NULL, 'Malaika beach resort', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@malaikabeachresort.com', 677001000, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Tunza Road, Mwanza', 'https://malaikabeachresort.com', '-', '', 'Caressed by the gentle waves of Lake Victoria in a secluded scenic spot (but minutes away from Mwanza’s airport and city center), Malaika is a distinctive high-end beach resort in Tanzania, specializing in beach tourism, business travel and weddings & conferences.\r\nOur hotel is built on an imposing rock foundation, which is also visible from inside the hotel. At our vast premises you’ll find a pool, wedding lawn, and many other facilities catering to families, vacationers and events of all sizes.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 14:46:38', '2024-08-08 14:46:38'),
(200, NULL, 'Gold crest hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'marketing@goldcresthotel.com', 677353500, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'PPF Tower, Kenyatta Rd, Mwanza', 'https://www.goldcresthotel.com', '-', '', 'Gold Crest Hotel Mwanza is a contemporary hotel centrally located in the heart of Mwanza city. Situated just 10km from the main airport, our establishment boasts modern rooms equipped with a comprehensive array of amenities. Additionally, our prime location offers guests convenient access to various commercial facilities, including banks and corporate offices. Committed to delivering exceptional high-quality services, we ensure a seamless and satisfying experience for our esteemed clientele.\r\nOur hotel is managed by professionals with long years of experience in the industry and its growth achieved through consistency and quality.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 18:42:09', '2024-08-08 18:42:09'),
(201, NULL, 'Mbeya  hotel limited', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'reservations@mbeyahotel.com', 719410628, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Kaunda Ave, Mbeya', 'https://mbeyahotel.co.tz', '-', '', 'Mbeya Hotel is 13-year old family-run business.\r\n\r\nIn 2005, we acquired Mbeya Hotel and began an exciting journey in the region’s tourism business. Our first clients were organisations whose staff travelled through Mbeya often. We were always remembered as the comfortable hotel that offered close proximity to Mbeya town.\r\n\r\nWe’re conveniently located in the heart of Mbeya\r\n\r\nThe Hotel provides transportation to and from the airport, and around Mbeya town. We also book Safaris. Our goal is to share memorable experiences with our guests.\r\nKaribu sana Mbeya!', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 18:46:18', '2024-08-08 18:46:18'),
(202, NULL, 'Mbeya forest hill motel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'support@booked.net', 678205224, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Tanzania-Zambia Highway National Road, Mbeya', 'https://mbeya-forest-hill-motel.booked.net', '-', '', 'Mbeya Forest Hill Motel lies 4300 feet away from Mbozi Meteorite, offering 40 rooms and featuring a free parking lot and an outdoor swimming pool. There is an airport shuttle bus service, 24-hour front desk and housekeeping service available at the property. \r\nThe venue is located within 10 minutes\' walk from the center of Mbeya. Ngozi Crater Lake is 20 minutes’ walk from this hotel.\r\nEvery room features a closet, a work desk and direct dial phone. A shower, free toiletries and towels can be found in the bathrooms.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 18:56:34', '2024-08-08 18:56:34'),
(203, NULL, 'Mbeya golden city hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'hgoldencity@gmail.com.xn--x77hma', 764054220, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Mbeya', 'Instagram https://www.instagram.com › golden_cityhotel', '-', '', 'The hotel is in a nice location. Has secure parking and the food is excellent especially if you want a taste of local food.\r\nThe rooms are not bad and you will be assured of a good rest. It is hustle free to get a room. The staff are all excellent - the give their service with a smile.\r\nSuch a wonderful place to think peaceful ....rooms are completely sound absorbing to make it so quite, to be honest that is one among many places that deserve being highly rated again and again for its marvelous hospitality.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:05:04', '2024-08-08 19:05:04'),
(204, NULL, 'Fun retreat resort', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@funretreat.com', 622999555, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Moshono, Arusha 10367', 'http://www.funretreat.com', '-', '', 'Located in Mbeya, within 4.3 km of Elegante Supermarket and 4.4 km of Shoppers Choice (Supermarket), Mbeya Golden City Hotel provides a terrace. The property is around 7 km from Mbeya bus station and 9 km from Mbeya Institute of Science and Technology. Free WiFi is available. The units in the hotel are equipped with a TV. Every room is equipped with a private bathroom with a shower and free toiletries. A continental breakfast is available every morning at the property. Staff at the reception can provide information on what to do in the area.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:13:54', '2024-08-08 19:13:54'),
(205, NULL, 'Kibo palace hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'sales@kibopalacehotel.com', 753036444, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'P. O. BOX 2523, Kibo Palace Hotel Arusha, Nyerere Road, ArushA, Tanzania', 'https://kibopalacehotel.com', '-', '', 'Named after the highest peak of Africa’s highest mountain – Mt Kilimanjaro, Kibo Palace Hotel is one of Arusha’s most exciting and innovative luxury hotels. Contemporary, conductive, and unconventional, a luxury hotel with a new attitude. The hotel is strategically located 45 minutes drive from Kilimanjaro Airport and a 10-minute walk to the central business district. Banking and hospital facilities are all within 50 meters radius of the hotel. The architectural design gives the hotel an authentic character of its own.\r\nWelcome to Kibo Palace Apartments your home away from home. We recognize and understand that where you choose to make your home is probably one of the most important decisions you will have to make in your life.\r\nWe, therefore, want to make this experience for you to be memorable and worthwhile. We are fully furnished.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:19:23', '2024-08-08 19:19:23');
