(206, NULL, 'Mount meru hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@mountmeruhotel.co.tz', 272970256, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Arusha-Taveta Road Sekei Area Arusha TZ, 2673', 'https://www.mountmeruhotel.co.tz', '-', '', 'Mount Meru Hotel, the Arusha’s famous hotel and Africa\'s largest and most exciting conference destination is a 178 room 5* luxurious hotel. An oasis of tranquility on the Tanzania’s gateway to major tour tourist destination, the Mount Meru Hotel blends stylishly elegant African architecture with supremely luxurious accommodation; sparkling water gardens with a beautifully landscaped gardens and a wide choice of international restaurants. Tanzania is renowned for being the gateway to the Serengeti and annually, thousands flock through its borders in order to (hopefully) glimpse the migrating herds of wildebeest across its famed plains and see one of the few truly natural hunting grounds where predator and prey are free to roam, graze and hunt uninhibited. What visitors to Tanzania are simply astounded by (something National Geographic does not always highlight) are the other fantastic locations and the warmth and inviting nature of the Tanzanian people.\r\n\r\nSituated at the foothills of Mount Meru in the city of Arusha, the Mount Meru Hotel lies on 15 acres of serene, lush and beautifully landscaped gardens incorporating a wide variety of indigenous trees, and offering sanctuary to a startling array of birds and butterflies. As the topographic centre piece of the Arusha National Park, the hotel is also surrounded by some of Africa’s most breathtaking vistas, rich with a diverse array of wildlife, etched against the fertile slopes of this beautiful mountain, the fifth highest peak in Africa.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:23:33', '2024-08-08 19:23:33'),
(207, NULL, 'Green mountain hotel', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@greenmountainhotel.co.tz', 765111119, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Arusha, Nelson Mandela Rd, Milla Ave', 'https://greenmountainhotel.co.tz', '-', '', 'Located in the heart of Arusha City, Green Mountain Hotel is an iconic nouveau masterpiece sitting at the Geneva of Africa which offers its guests a hospitable & sumptuous accommodation. Enjoy flavorsome international cuisines prepared by our excellent chefs. Our extensive & top-notch facilities, exclusive suites, Simba restaurant, a fascinating & serene pool, an exquisite & magical garden perfect for your safari getaway which will make you carry on enjoyable memories forever.\r\nBreathe fresh air & gaze over the beautiful city of Arusha. Enjoy our luxurious rooms each filled with carefully curated facilities to make your stay delightful. Enjoy our quick & wonderful services from our friendly staff.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:28:35', '2024-08-08 19:28:35'),
(208, NULL, 'Trust tour and safari Tanzania', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'ombenikiware@gmail.com', 763473832, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Africa and Arusha-Tanzania', 'https://trusttourstz.com', '-', '', 'Trust Tours and Safaris Company, a top tour operator located in Arusha, Tanzania, has been offering exceptional services since its establishment in 2008. Being recognized for its excellence, the company has been nominated for world travel awards in both 2023 and 2024. With offices in Nungwi, Zanzibar, and Nairobi, Kenya, Trust Tours and Safaris Company is renowned for organizing unforgettable safari experiences. They provide customized packages for both mid-range and luxury adventures, such as wildlife safaris and mountain climbs of Kilimanjaro and Mount Meru. For an unparalleled exploration of East Africa, Trust Tours and Safaris Company is a reliable choice.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:34:08', '2024-08-08 19:34:08'),
(209, NULL, 'Car rentals tour and safaris Mbeya airport', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@mbeyacity.com', 652411487, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Kabwe street, Mbeya 1402', 'https://tz.linkedin.com › car-rental', '-', '', 'he cost of MBI airport car rental varies based on factors such as the type of car, the rental duration, and the time of year. With Expedia, you can find competitive MBI airport car rentals to match your needs and preferences. Keep in mind that prices can fluctuate, so we recommend booking MBI airport cars in advance to secure the best deals.\r\nRenting a car at Mbeya can greatly enhance your travel experience. Having a car at your disposal gives you the freedom to explore at your own pace, whether you\'re heading to a specific destination or planning to explore the area. Plus, MBI airport cars are convenient and easy to book, with a wide range of options to suit your MBI airport rental needs and budget.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 19:50:49', '2024-08-08 19:50:49'),
(210, NULL, 'Tali 24hrs travel company limited', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'tali24hrstravel@gmail.com', 784677155, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Nyerere Road,Moil Petrol Station, Mwanza Tanzania 11956', 'https://www.facebook.com › 24HRS-Travel-Company', '-', '', 'Since Tali 24hrs Travel has opened its doors for business many years ago, our goal in providing customer service with a high standard has never been changed. We do this by offering our lowest cost price, taking all the fuss in planning your travel and to make sure no loose ends are left tagging behind. In addition, we provide numerous services that go beyond what other travel agencies offer in the market.\r\nOur services include the following:\r\n-Air Travel - Domestic & International\r\n-Package Tours & Safaris\r\n-Hotel Bookings\r\n-Car Hire\r\n-Air Charters\r\n-Sight and Local Attractions\r\n-Travel Insurance -Shuttle Service -Visa .', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 20:02:41', '2024-08-08 20:02:41'),
(211, NULL, 'Air Tanzania company limited', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@airtanzania.co.tz', 748773900, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'P.O.BOX 543 Dar-es-Salaam Tanzania,  ATC House, Second Floor, Ohio Street,  Dar Es Salaam', 'https://www.airtanzania.co.tz', '-', '20240808150956.png', 'Dodoma is Tanzania’s capital city located right at the center of the country, allowing easy accessibility to all other regions of Tanzania. The history of the city shares a lot with construction of the Tanzania central railway in 1907 by Germans, and was announced to be the capital city by the government of Tanzania in 1970. Dodoma city hosts the House of Parliament, Dodoma Cathedral and the Muammar Gaddafi Mosque. The dry earth and sandy soil of the surrounding Dodoma region is perfect for wine growing and is home to a number of vineyards producing red and white varieties of Chenin Blanc, Shiraz, Cabernet and Sauvignon. Hang out at the ‘Mnadani’ Barbeque spot (Nyama Choma) every Saturday and enjoy the hospitality of the dominant “Gogo” culture.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 20:09:56', '2024-08-08 20:09:56'),
(212, NULL, 'Asili travel and tour company ltd', NULL, '-', 31, 216, 'info@asiliadventuresafaris.com', 222600334, NULL, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, NULL, 'Dar es Salaam', 'https://www.asiliadventuresafaris.com', '-', '', 'Welcome to ASILI ADVENTURE & SAFARIS LIMITED – a company founded on Excellence, Integrity and Passion: Passion for what we do, Passion for people, Passion for Wildlife, Passion for Africa and the World. Asili Adventure safaris Ltd is one of the most sought for operators in East Africa offering personalized quality service and affordable tailor-made holidays that suit your individual requirements and budget without compromising on quality.\r\n\r\nWe committed to ensuring that every client has an outstanding and memorable trip by engaging the best guides, ensuring the best travel modes, and booking the best hotels and lodges. For the African holiday traveller, Asili Adventure Safaris Ltd offers a full range of options including luxury safaris, custom safari, Kenya wildlife tour, budget accommodated tours, Indian Ocean beach vacation holidays, walking safaris, Mountain climbing in Kenya and Tanzania, family holiday safaris Tours, balloon safaris.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '0', NULL, '2024-08-08 20:20:11', '2024-08-08 20:20:11'),
